channel.title: Need a person to be my coding partner
channel.description:
I'm looking for a person to develop a server with. You must be experienced in java, delta, and 317's. Pm me through skype if you would like to be my programming partner! Thanks -Vudu
P.S. I already have a client and source I've been working on; we would just continue working on it together. I'm experienced too so don't think you'll be doin all the work!
My Skype: Cmhatton96

item.title: Need a person to be my coding partner
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

We do not condone these types of posts. If you want to create a development team, you’re going to need to put more effort in. Otherwise, we do not appreciate people wanting work done, without putting in any effort themselves.
